As a (Big) Data Scientist I have a strong passion for developing Data Models, Dashboards, Reports and Performance related insights. With Data Science experience I can perform advanced analytics to large data sets (I find patterns and dependencies naturally).
There is no place for any misscommunication - I can present the results of my work in an intuitive and understandable way for the stakeholders.

I would like to become a Data Science Specialist in the future, that's why I'm so motivated to learn.

Hard skills: Python, SQL, Excel, PowerBI, Tableau.